<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to the ${MallName} Team!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header img {
            max-height: 50px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .title {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        a {
            color: #1e90ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #ffa500;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/mSfk5z2/vm-logo-new.png" alt="${MallName} Logo">
        <p class="title">Welcome Aboard!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Dear ${CustomerName},</h2>
        <p>We're excited to welcome you to the ${MallName} team! You have been assigned to our ${branch} branch. Your account has been created by ${AdminName}, and you are all set to start your new journey with us.</p>
        <p>Here are your initial login details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Username: ${email}</li>
            <li>Password: ${password}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please access your account using the following link: <a href="${loginurl}" class="button">Login to My Account</a></p>
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> Upon logging in for the first time, you will be prompted to set a new, unique password. As every action on our site is tagged with your name, it is crucial to maintain the security of your account.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Welcome to the team, and here's to a successful partnership at the ${branch} branch!</p>
        <p>Warm regards,</p>
        <p>${AdminName}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        Â© ${Year} ${MallName}. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
